high_descs: Walk down the passage and turn right to enter the bedroom to face the bed.
Pick up the black pot from the bed.
Turn around to walk out the room on the left and turn left on the passage and reach the fridge on the right.
Cool the pot in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the pot on the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot on the left sink.

high_descs: Go straight and take the first right into the bedroom, and go right towards the bed.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Leave the room the way you came in, turn left and then take the first right into the kitchen area with the fridge.
Place the pot in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Place the pot on the drainboard next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cool a pot in a fridge and place it on a kitchen sink.

high_descs: Go straight turn right to the bed
Pick the pot from the bed
Exit from the room turn left then turn right to the fridge
Put the pot into the fridge cool it and take it back
Place the pot near to the sink
anns.task_desc: Pick the pot from the bed,clean it and place it near to the sink
